 surface volatiles. We also compare 209P/LINEAR to other low\nactivity comets, where evidence for a diversity of the origin of low activity\nis seen.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Sep 2015 04:37:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-07"}
